data.description: Wonderful end-unit townhome features private setting, soaring ceilings, loft area and many updates to include new flooring, paint and trim throughout. Kitchen updates include newer countertops, backsplash and stainless appliances. Spacious loft area overlooks the living room. Enjoy the upper level laundry closet to include high-end washer and dryer. Primary bedroom features vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet and access to the updated bathroom. Enjoy the private patio just off the kitchen area. Roofs and driveways are all newer with no assessment to the homeowner.
